The '''Beatrice Prisen''' was founded in 1983 by Birthe and Paul Beckett. The prize is awarded annually by the [[Danish Academy]], it is currently DKK 50,000. The prize is handed to an author who writes either lyrics or prose, and whose "published books already have a quality, which there is reason to appreciate, and where there is reason to believe, that he or she will develop further."<ref>[http://www.danskeakademi.dk/priser/vispriser.asp?id=26 Danskeakademi.dk]</ref>
