The '''Brigade Mixte Mobile''' ('''BMM''') is the [[paramilitary]] [[secret police]] of [[Cameroon]]. Headquarters are in [[N'Kondengue]], near the capital of [[Yaoundé]].<ref>[https://books.google.co.uk/books?id=D-1eCwAAQBAJ&lpg=PA36&ots=C8dLSOpMgG&dq=Brigade%20Mixte%20Mobile&hl=nl&pg=PA36#v=onepage&q=Brigade%20Mixte%20Mobile&f=false John Andrade, World Police & Paramilitary Forces, pag. 36.]</ref>

The brigade operates a number of prisons for political prisoners in the country.

